"This is an overview of device handling in Qubes OS. For specific devices "
"([block](/doc/how-to-use-block-storage-devices/), [USB](/doc/how-to-use-usb-"
"devices/) and [PCI](/doc/how-to-use-pci-devices/) devices), please visit "
"their respective pages."
msgstr ""

#: ../../_doc/user/how-to-guides/how-to-use-devices.md:18
#: e430e2fdbcb04543bd1152124226981a
msgid ""
"**Important security warning:** Device handling comes with many security "
"implications. Please make sure you carefully read and understand the "
"**[security considerations](/doc/device-handling-security/)**."
msgstr ""

