msgstr ""

#: ../../_doc/user/how-to-guides/how-to-use-devices.md:59
#: 053e91fd57304b1e9c03bb1239bb779b
msgid ""
"Only `mic` should be attached to more than one running VM. You may *assign* "
"a device to more than one VM (using the `--persistent` option), however, "
"only one of them can be started at the same time."
msgstr ""

#: ../../_doc/user/how-to-guides/how-to-use-devices.md:62
#: fc0c4abb29ab4a539a04b729520189eb
msgid ""
"But be careful: There is a [bug in `qvm-device block` or `qvm-"
"block`](https://github.com/QubesOS/qubes-issues/issues/4692) which will "
"allow you to *attach* a block device to two running VMs. Don't do that!"
msgstr ""

